reviews.text:
One of the best korean all u can eat restaurant in town. Even Higher A la carte standard! So many selection.

Especial the pork belly n ginseng chicken soup.... and also deep fried chicken. 

Seat is good n the deco s cute. Cheap price for such a big meal. V ordered another army hot pot for $40. The bill is $440 included service charge! Nice n cheap

My husband already said need to bookmark this and ll come back again.

I have tried the buffet in the restaurant. Most of the food was good but the drilled meats were poor. The main dish that could be ordered in the buffet set was in regular size. So, think before you order. Haha
Nice food and serves is good
The food is OK. Fried Chicken is Crispy. I booked the table though eatigo so the price is reasonable.
Not interesting for the price. Its not cheap for the taste you get. Korean fried chicken is also not up to part. Quite the same as KFC or even worse than KFC.

reviews.text:

Especial the pork belly n ginseng chicken soup.... and also deep fried chicken. 

Seat is good n the deco s cute. Cheap price for such a big meal. V ordered another army hot pot for $40. The bill is $440 included service charge! Nice n cheap

My husband already said need to bookmark this and ll come back again.
地方舒適食物好味， 尤其是三款沙律我同朋友都喜歡食

男友放工同佢食晚餐，我們選了這間我同朋友黎過的韓式餐廳。
環境好好，舒服寬敞又靚靚可愛設計，有好多星星、卡通圖案及花花擺設，好令人開心的感覺！
原來宜家有一個放題，有火鍋/主菜/沙拉/小食/湯類/甜點等等，200幾就可以食所有韓國菜，正喔！
我們點了一個大蝦沙律（蝦好爽脆，沙律蔬菜多又新鮮翠綠，紅紅的車厘茄，配上麻醬，好味道又健康！）
韓式冷麵（好推薦的，爽脆片片梨子，好爽甜清涼、爽脆青瓜條、冷麵好香好滑，更配上半邊蛋喔）[得意]
韓式柚子炸雞翼（柚子汁一碟，可自行加上，點上了更清新更中和油膩感；炸雞翼賣相靚，外脆內嫩嫩雞肉）[色]
Lunch 去唔錯，食物有水準。可返食

I have tried the buffet in the restaurant. Most of the food was good but the drilled meats were poor. The main dish that could be ordered in the buffet set was in regular size. So, think before you order. Haha
